NEW DELHI, August 6 (Xinhua) -- Deposed Fiji Prime Minister
Mahendra Chaudhry, who was released last month after being held
hostage for eight weeks by rebel leader George Speight, will visit
India on August 17, Prime Minister Atal Bihari Vajpayee said
