<TEXT>
<P>
MACAO, August 6 (Xinhua) -- United States crushed the fighting
Japanese in straight sets in the final day at the 1.04 million-US-
dollar World Women's Volleyball Grand Prix Macao's leg here on
Sunday.
</P>
<P>
With the superiority of height and power, the Americans did not
meet much trouble by outclassing the Japanese 25-18, 25-17 and 26-
24 with powerful spikes and firm blocks.
</P>
<P>
